            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;Tier 1+2+3: reasoning share, Claude 5h billing window detector, subagent attribution, tool-call cost breakdown, 365-day activity heatmap, click-through anomaly drill-in, cross-tool cost projection. Two new themes (Aurora, Noise) plus the picker curated to seven. License flip to AGPL-3.0-only. See full notes on GitHub.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
